{"tid":2102654,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"喊能左！原來部分票站有紙張選票，聽日初選可以投熱血公民了！！！！！","createTime":"2020-07-10T15:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T06:49:37.000Z","uid":73381,"like":20,"dislike":92,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f18a5ccf4c63430829558b42828b7cccf84659","tid":2102654,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:23:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=1Tc6dc_1R-BuPNl2p1_x5VA864A3Crzrn&amp;ll=22.35912066705347%2C114.10494750000001&amp;z=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F0%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1Tc6dc_1R-BuPNl2p1_x5VA864A3Crzrn%26ll%3D22.35912066705347%252C114.10494750000001%26z%3D11&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=8770ac24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=1Tc6dc_1R-BuPNl2p1_x5VA864A3Crzrn&amp;ll=22.35912066705347%2C114.10494750000001&amp;z=11</a><br />\n<br />\n去上面條link個地圖搵有設紙張選票嘅票站 去到唔使講啦 即刻問職員拎選票 <br />\n跟住係選票上大大隻字寫你想投嘅嗰位熱氣公民侯選人名字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港島區：<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">莊芷菌(莊子)，鄭鋪滿(四眼)</span></span><br />\n新界西：<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">鄭松秦(秦搏)</span></span><br />\n新界東：<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">黃逃健(健哥)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家記住！<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">有熱血投熱血，冇熱血投本土！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"18a31a45d0375787ed5c1e3858d7b5c66005e475","tid":2102654,"uid":73381,"like":30,"dislike":5,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"熱血公民 可以代表我 可以為我永續基本法<br />\n假使可以 五區當選<br />\n錦滿會打交 松泰負責投下反對票<br />\n這樣議事很足夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f656e7faba3c2c9d85600a8a502bca0cb5d71658","tid":2102654,"uid":5649,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6